faqs.title: What is the date of the event?
faqs.answer: The event will be held from July 20-22, 2024.

faqs.title: Is there a cost to attend?
faqs.answer: The event is free to attend, but registration is required.

faqs.title: Who should attend?
faqs.answer: Developers of all levels, software engineers, tech enthusiasts, and anyone interested in the latest trends in software development.

faqs.title: Will the sessions be recorded?
faqs.answer: Yes, all sessions will be recorded and available to registered attendees after the event.

faqs.title: How can I network with other attendees?
faqs.answer: Our virtual platform includes chat rooms, discussion boards, and scheduled networking sessions to connect with fellow attendees.
